snippet.textDisplay:
Bangla is the sweetest language in the entire world. Fullstop. 
Let us all keep this beautiful language alive
May we never let out beautiful language and culture die
Aaj kal onek poshchim bonger bangali ra Bangla bhule jacche
Bangla culture bhule jacche
Hindi kotha bolte chaiche, hindi culture follow korye chaiche
It is sad. Ami onek Bangali der ke ek aponer sathe Hindi te kotha bolte dekhechi, Hindi te kotha kano? Amar Bangla ki more gache? 
Amar satheo onek Bangali ra Hindi te kotha bolte ase, aar ami sudu Bangla te uttor di, amar bhasha akhono beche ache
Jokhon proyojon porbe, tokhon ami Hindi te kotha bolbo tar chara amar Hindi te kotha bole ko faida? 
We must keep our beautiful language alive
We must keep our beautiful culture alive
Joy Hind
Joy Bangla
🇮🇳❤️🇧🇩
